'''William Schmollinger''' (''fl''. 1830s) was a famous cartographer.{{citation needed|date=March 2013}}

He engraved a map of [[Hertfordshire]] with [[Thomas Moule]], commonly known as ''Moule's Map of Hertfordshire''.<ref>{{cite web|title=W. Schmollinger's Map of Hertfordshire|url=http://www.hertfordshire-genealogy.co.uk/data/maps/schmollinger-1845.htm|accessdate=2 March 2013|date=November 2008}}</ref>

